    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://newyork.craigslist.org/que/fbh/6046253912.html"></div>
        </div>
We are currently seeking an experienced Cook for our educational location in Briarwood.<br>
<br>
Monday - Friday<br>
6am - 2:30pm<br>
<br>
Essential Duties and Responsibilities:<br>
Prepare high-quality food items according to standardized recipes and instructions to meet production, delivery and service standards<br>
Serves meals or prepares for delivery by using correct portioning, meeting outlined standards, ensuring that food is at the correct temperature<br>
Cleans kitchen after preparation and serving, maintaining high standards of cleanliness. Stores or discards excess food in accordance with safe food-handling procedures.<br>
Keeps refrigerators and storerooms clean and neat. Ensures food and supply items are stored per company standards<br>
Operates and maintains kitchen equipment as instructed<br>
Assists in production planning, record keeping and reporting as required<br>
Assists in the ordering and receiving of all food and supplies as required<br>
Performs job safely while maintaining a clean, safe work environment<br>
Performs other duties as assigned<br>
<br>
Candidates should have:<br>
At least 2-3 years of experience<br>
Great customer service and knife skills are required<br>
A desire to serve our guests with a smile and a quick hand<br>
Professional appearance and pride in service is necessary<br>
Must be a team player with outstanding customer service skills with the ability to excel in a fast paced environment<br>
Be able to work alone, think on your feet and hold responsibility for presentation and service<br>
Must be detail oriented and timely<br>
Education in Culinary or Restaurant management is extremely helpful<br>
<br>
We offer competitive wages, benefits and a respectful work environment with room for growth. <br>
<br>
If you possess these skills and would like to be considered, please reply with resume and contact information.    </section>

